280
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,600
I'm new here.

281
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,000
If he doesn't bully me, that's already pretty good.

282
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:58,870
Mr. Fang,

283
00:11:59,070 --> 00:12:00,790
please guide me in the future

284
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:02,010
and take me under your wing.

285
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,040
Come on.

286
00:12:03,350 --> 00:12:04,390
I'm not out yet.

287
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,840
Wait until I'm out before you bully him.

288
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,480
From now on, he's your master.

289
00:12:08,730 --> 00:12:09,970
If he really bullies you, let me know.

290
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:11,510
Alright, you guys chat.

291
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,080
I see.

292
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:12,650
I see, Mr. Tao.

293
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,040
Okay.

294
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:14,530
I wouldn't dare. He's all muscle.

295
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,190
Master,

296
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,570
I have a desk outside.

297
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,150
How about I...

298
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:21,870
go out to work?

299
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:22,600
Wait a minute.

300
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:23,310
Let me emphasize two things:

301
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:24,770
First, never call me "master" again.

302
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:25,390
When you call me master,

303
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:26,860
I get a bit full of myself

304
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:28,000
and forget my name.

305
00:12:28,300 --> 00:12:29,350
Just call me Chen Shuo.

306
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:30,100
Of course,

307
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,390
if you feel uncomfortable calling me by name

308
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,110
since I'm your senior,

309
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:32,900
just call me Mr. Chen,

310
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,200
alright?

311
00:12:35,010 --> 00:12:35,480
As for the second point,

312
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,790
look, this room is so big.

313
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,410
It's just me here, all alone,

314
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,390
and it's really boring.

315
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:40,390
It's good that you're here.

316
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:42,120
Just move your stuff in directly.

317
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,240
We'll each have a desk.

318
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:44,780
So that we can discuss things easily. Is that okay?

319
00:12:46,230 --> 00:12:47,360
Go get your stuff. Hurry up and move in.

320
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:50,860
Alright, I'll go get my stuff.

321
00:12:59,120 --> 00:12:59,670
Libo.

322
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:05,360
Tian.

323
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:06,980
Mr. Chen.

324
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,550
Are you tired?

325
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:09,590
I'm okay.

326
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,600
I'm waking myself up.

327
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:12,620
Your brain is sharp enough even if you don't wake yourself up.

328
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:15,580
Let me tell you something.

329
00:13:15,950 --> 00:13:17,550
I was planning to tell you after I make it,

330
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,510
but it looks like

331
00:13:18,530 --> 00:13:19,550
that's not going to happen.

332
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,510
But I have to tell you

333
00:13:20,610 --> 00:13:21,730
so you'll know how I feel.

334
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,630
What is it?

335
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,960
Actually, I've been

336
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,250
looking for a partner at our firm.

337
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:27,550
Otherwise,

338
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,910
I'd be sitting alone in my office,

339
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,020
feeling lonely

340
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,280
and bored, right?
-Yes.

341
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:33,280
Why do I always chat with you?

342
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,750
You're sharp and capable.

343
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,780
Right? We'd make a great team.

344
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,030
However,

345
00:13:40,450 --> 00:13:41,780
today the firm assigned me a partner.

346
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:42,750
Who is it?

347
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:44,320
The one who's packing his things.

348
00:13:46,610 --> 00:13:47,850
I've been here for a while

349
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,920
and didn't even notice him.

350
00:13:48,950 --> 00:13:49,950
Who is he?

351
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,280
Ms. Fang's nephew.

352
00:13:53,300 --> 00:13:55,020
He doesn't even have a lawyer's qualification.

353
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,320
He's been here for a year

354
00:13:56,450 --> 00:13:57,600
and hasn't worked on any cases.

355
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,840
He hasn't even passed the qualification exam yet.

356
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:01,080
Then he must be a good kid.

357
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,590
Why did they assign him to me? Are they blind?

358
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:05,190
Mr. Chen, I have to warn you.

359
00:14:05,590 --> 00:14:06,200
He could be

360
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:07,670
a spy for Ms. Fang,

361
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:09,660
planted by him on your side.

362
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,200
A spy?

363
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:13,970
Come on. You're so funny, Tian.

364
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:15,410
Be careful.

365
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,840
You're back.

366
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,120
What are you looking at so seriously?

367
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,010
Wait.

368
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,940
When I came back, both of you weren't here.

369
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,870
Where did you go?

370
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,280
I went to meet a client,

371
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,150
introduced by my senior.

372
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:32,530
It's also helping us expand our client base.

373
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:34,060
By the way,

374
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:36,170
I inquired about Liangcheng Law Firm.

375
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,750
In He Qiaohui's case,

376
00:14:37,780 --> 00:14:39,400
our opponent turned out to be Han.

377
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,490
I can't believe it's not Chen Shuo, but Han.

378
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:43,590
What could Han possibly do?

379
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,080
You could figure it out without even thinking.

380
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,630
He'll stall.

381
00:14:47,890 --> 00:14:48,680
Just wait and see.

382
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:50,510
It'll probably take

383
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,720
3 to 5 months just to serve the summons.

384
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:53,940
That won't do.

385
00:14:54,290 --> 00:14:56,850
He can stall, but Auntie Song can't afford to wait.

386
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:59,320
How is Auntie Song going to manage those 3 to 5 months?

387
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,180
Not to mention, her husband

388
00:15:00,210 --> 00:15:01,660
is still in the hospital.

389
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:03,810
I just don't understand.

390
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,150
We just filed the case the day before yesterday,

391
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:09,790
and yesterday they already went to find Han.

392
00:15:10,330 --> 00:15:12,450
Logically, they shouldn't know about it yet.

393
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,120
You're back.

394
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,390
Luo.

395
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,270
Qiu.

396
00:15:21,190 --> 00:15:22,070
Can I take a leave?

397
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,030
What happened?

398
00:15:23,530 --> 00:15:25,130
My family called just now,

399
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,120
saying my mom's in the hospital.

400
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:27,690
Well...

401
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:28,910
That's a big deal.

402
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,030
You should head home right away.

403
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:30,950
But...

404
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,930
I just took on Auntie Song's case.

405
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,720
Don't worry about it.

406
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,420
At worst, Qiu Hua and I can handle it.

407
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:38,710
Go and be with your mom.

408
00:15:39,310 --> 00:15:40,740
When I took on the case,

409
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:41,900
I said I'd handle it.

410
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,270
I don't want to delay your business.

411
00:15:44,870 --> 00:15:46,960
Which is more important, your mom or the case?

412
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:47,750
At a time like this,

413
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,000
you don't have to fight alone.

414
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,000
Just go.

415
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:51,080
Okay.

416
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:58,480
By the way, Luo.

417
00:15:58,910 --> 00:16:00,750
Auntie Song has already told He Qiaohui

418
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:01,790
about the lawsuit.

419
00:16:01,790 --> 00:16:03,360
She thought that this way, she could get her to pay back voluntarily.

420
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:05,060
Remember to contact her.

421
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:09,190
Who told Auntie Song to tell He Qiaohui?

422
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:11,820
Didn't I repeatedly tell her to keep it confidential?

423
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:13,640
Yes.

424
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:15,530
It was me.

425
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,210
I'm sorry, Qiu.

426
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:20,280
I didn't know you had told her that.

427
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:22,380
I thought we were suing openly

428
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:24,040
and didn't need to keep it confidential.

429
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,840
I'm speechless, Xia Shu.

430
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:27,160
Go home and be with your mom now.

431
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:28,180
Just go now.

432
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:29,250
Yes, go back now.

433
00:16:29,530 --> 00:16:31,480
You haven't spent all that 800,000, have you?

434
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:32,250
Do you have money?

435
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:33,030
Yes.

436
00:16:33,210 --> 00:16:34,210
Then hurry up and go back.

437
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:35,800
Go.

438
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,680
Be careful.

439
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:38,040
Okay.

440
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:39,440
Tell us when you arrive.

441
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,600
I don't know what to say.

442
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:52,600
I've only just started finding her likable recently,

443
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,730
and now she's caused us trouble again.

444
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,480
In her world, there's always sunshine.

445
00:16:57,590 --> 00:17:00,120
How could she feel the darkness of human nature?

446
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:02,050
But there's no need to rush.

447
00:17:02,310 --> 00:17:04,190
Life itself will teach her anyway.

448
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,000
Master.

449
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:09,069
See? You forgot again.

450
00:17:10,349 --> 00:17:11,740
Oh, right. Mr. Chen.

451
00:17:15,329 --> 00:17:16,770
Mr. Chen, actually...

452
00:17:17,339 --> 00:17:18,849
I don't have my lawyer's qualification yet.

453
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:21,880
So I may not be able to help you with some important things.

454
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,990
But for small things within my ability, feel free to call on me.

455
00:17:24,020 --> 00:17:25,150
No problem.

456
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:29,200
Fang Rui.

457
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:31,440
We'll be partners from now on,

458
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,430
so I'll be straightforward.

459
00:17:32,450 --> 00:17:33,790
I heard some gossip.

460
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,350
Is Fang Lihong...

461
00:17:35,830 --> 00:17:37,030
your aunt?

462
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:40,000
Who told you that?

463
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:40,790
Is she?

464
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,280
Really?

465
00:17:43,310 --> 00:17:44,130
Who told you that?

466
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,360
Han Zhitong, Mr. Han.

467
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:49,270
Don't worry about it.

468
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,330
Mr. Han.

469
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:54,380
Fang Rui,

470
00:17:55,050 --> 00:17:56,290
well, let's keep it like this from now on.

471
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,200
If I need you, I'll definitely call you.

472
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,200
If there's nothing,

473
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:01,590
just sit here and focus on preparing for your qualification exam.

474
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:02,750
-Okay.
-And,

475
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:04,210
if we earn money from any case,

476
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:04,930
don't worry,

477
00:18:05,130 --> 00:18:06,370
I won't leave you out, okay?

478
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:07,710
Well, Master.

479
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:09,410
Mr. Chen,

480
00:18:09,430 --> 00:18:10,630
I'm not here for money.

481
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,450
So you're here to keep an eye on me for your aunt?

482
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:14,390
What does that mean?

483
00:18:14,410 --> 00:18:15,330
Just kidding.

484
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,940
I'm here to learn from you.

485
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:20,680
My parents teach law at university,

486
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:22,140
and my aunt...

487
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,640
well, is a lawyer.

488
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:25,600
They think I should also

489
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:26,910
be a lawyer in the future.

490
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:28,880
But...

491
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,000
When I was applying to university,

492
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:31,230
my parents forced me to change my intended major.

493
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:32,550
Then after graduation,

494
00:18:32,610 --> 00:18:33,930
all my classmates passed the bar exam,

495
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,000
but I didn't.

496
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,930
My parents think I embarrassed them.

497
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:39,160
Then my aunt brought me here,

498
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,680
to escape my parents

499
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:42,970
and focus on studying this.

500
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,890
It seems like you don't like law either.

501
00:18:47,110 --> 00:18:48,110
Law...

502
00:18:48,350 --> 00:18:49,160
is boring and monotonous.

503
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,560
It's all about winning or losing.

504
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:52,880
But life isn't all about winning and losing.

505
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,440
It's not a battle.

506
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,430
That's true.

507
00:18:57,350 --> 00:18:58,640
So what do you like?

508
00:18:59,270 --> 00:18:59,720
Painting,

509
00:19:00,290 --> 00:19:01,100
singing, and dancing.

510
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,720
When I have money, I like traveling;

511
00:19:03,740 --> 00:19:05,060
when I don't, I like staying home.

512
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,400
My dad says

513
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,400
that whatever costs money,

514
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,470
that's what I love.

515
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:11,050
So you like money.

516
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:12,000
Looks like we have similar interests.

517
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,270
Do you know what my nickname is?

518
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,790
My nickname is "Money String."

519
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:16,700
I really love money.

520
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:18,960
We'll definitely get along well in the future.

521
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:26,110
Ms. Yu,

522
00:19:26,130 --> 00:19:29,000
about He Qiaohui's case,

523
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:30,480
our client

524
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:32,270
is now in a difficult situation

525
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:34,080
and can't wait any longer.

526
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:36,680
Do you think it's possible to arrange the hearing as soon as possible?

527
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,340
We can't arrange it yet.

528
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:39,770
The summons hasn't even been served.

529
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,400
Isn't she in this city?

530
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:43,930
A few days ago, she even hired an attorney.

531
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,440
We've tried everything but still couldn't serve it.

532
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:47,580
She rejected our calls,

533
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:49,310
returned our mail,

534
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,600
and when we went to her place to deliver it,

535
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:52,730
the neighbors said they no longer live there.

536
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,160
Could you provide

537
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,240
a reliable address for delivery

538
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:58,720
or accurate contact information of the defendant?

539
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:02,400
We can't just sit back and wait.

540
00:20:02,830 --> 00:20:04,440
How about I contact Mr. Zhou

541
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:06,160
to see if I can find a breakthrough?

542
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:07,270
That works.

543
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:09,650
Both of us spending so much time with Auntie Song

544
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:10,760
is not cost-effective.

545
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:11,880
How about this?

546
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,350
I'll take Auntie Song around

547
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,650
and see if we can find

548
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,230
any other addresses of He Qiaohui.

549
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,240
But we need to hurry.

550
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,550
I don't think Uncle Li

551
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,350
can wait much longer.

552
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,160
Yingzi.

553
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:28,920
Mr. Zhou.

554
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:29,550
Mr. Zhou.

555
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:30,480
You haven't needed me for a long time.

556
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,960
Have you forgotten me?

557
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,110
If it weren't for some urgent matters,

558
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:35,520
I wouldn't dare trouble you.

559
00:20:35,550 --> 00:20:37,000
You're so busy with your business.

560
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:39,230
Did you find out anything about

561
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:40,420
what I asked you yesterday?

562
00:20:40,450 --> 00:20:41,410
You called me over so quickly.

563
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:43,310
Yes, yes.

564
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,350
Have a seat.

565
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:50,830
Look.

566
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:53,420
I took a look yesterday.

567
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:56,810
He Qiaohui and her husband

568
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,280
are definitely shady people.

569
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:01,400
That Shengmao Credit of theirs is a business

570
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,920
all about charging sky-high interest rates and discounting loans.

571
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:05,230
The money they borrow from her

572
00:21:05,250 --> 00:21:06,560
is all life-saving money.

573
00:21:06,970 --> 00:21:07,860
The people she scams

574
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:09,580
are workers and small business owners.

575
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:11,160
They've scammed so many people?

576
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:12,680
Why don't they sue them?

577
00:21:12,810 --> 00:21:14,680
It's lucky if she doesn't sue them.

578
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:18,000
She either forces them to mortgage their houses in advance

579
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:19,890
or has them find some close relatives

580
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:20,880
to vouch for them.

581
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:22,090
Who dares to sue her?

582
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,420
They might even beg her not to file a lawsuit.

583
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:25,480
And besides, these people don't have money.

584
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:28,480
They won't choose to go to court.

585
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:29,750
Mr. Zhou,

586
00:21:30,250 --> 00:21:32,140
you've really helped me a lot.

587
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,810
With these materials,

588
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,750
even if they can't be used directly as evidence,

589
00:21:38,010 --> 00:21:40,140
they'll make it easier for me to communicate with the judge in the future.

590
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:43,700
By the way, there's one more thing.

591
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:44,670
It's not urgent,

592
00:21:44,870 --> 00:21:46,260
but I need you to keep it in mind.

593
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:48,510
I want to gather as much information

594
00:21:48,510 --> 00:21:50,120
as possible about the victims.

595
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,680
It might come in handy down the road.

596
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:54,580
Sure, I'll ask around.

597
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:10,090
Could you help us check on her husband,

598
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:11,510
Zhou Damin?

599
00:22:11,790 --> 00:22:14,460
We've provided some information about him in our investigation letter.

600
00:22:12,710 --> 00:22:14,330
[Jingbei Real Estate Registration and Trading Center]

601
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:15,200
Okay.

602
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:19,110
There are two properties under Zhou Damin's name.

603
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:22,790
How is that possible?

604
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:24,000
The last time,

605
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:26,060
those two knelt in front of me,

606
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:29,110
asking me to lend them the only 500,000 I had.

607
00:22:29,220 --> 00:22:30,620
They said they were at their wits' end

608
00:22:31,230 --> 00:22:33,100
and didn't even have money for food.

609
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:36,680
Hello, Ms. Yu.

610
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,350
I'm Qiu Hua.

611
00:22:38,370 --> 00:22:40,170
I have something to report to you.

612
00:22:40,610 --> 00:22:42,650
He Qiaohui's husband, Zhou Damin,

613
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,330
owns two more properties.

614
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,290
I just wanted to ask if you

615
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:47,710
sent summonses to these two property addresses as well.

616
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,810
You mean this is the only way?

617
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,720
A public notice?

618
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:56,080
But with a public notice,

619
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:58,270
we'd at least have to wait two months.

620
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,240
With Auntie Song in her current situation,

621
00:23:00,260 --> 00:23:01,350
can she afford to wait?

622
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:02,470
We have no choice.

623
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,570
It's all thanks to Xia Shu.

624
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:06,800
How about I

625
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,380
accompany Auntie Song for a couple of days?

626
00:23:08,450 --> 00:23:10,110
It doesn't matter whether I do it or you do it.

627
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:11,010
I'll do it.

628
00:23:11,410 --> 00:23:12,780
Let me do it.

629
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,810
I'm suitable for running errands.

630
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:17,980
You're just afraid I'll take out my anger on Xia Shu.

631
00:23:18,950 --> 00:23:20,320
I just feel for her.

632
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,060
I've been through what Xia Shu

633
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:23,750
is going through now before.

634
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:26,640
These are the taxi fares for running errands with Auntie Song.

635
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,220
Ms. Luo, please reimburse me.

636
00:23:28,250 --> 00:23:28,900
Wait.

637
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:30,290
Why did you take taxis?

638
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:31,750
Doesn't your husband have a car?

639
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:34,600
Quanquan's family paid for that car.

640
00:23:34,850 --> 00:23:36,240
If I always drive it,

641
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,570
it'll be inappropriate if my mother-in-law finds out.

642
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,440
What's wrong with you?

643
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:41,940
You two are married now,

644
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:43,920
and there's no prenup.

645
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:46,310
What's his is yours, and what's yours is his.

646
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,570
In the future, it'll be all yours.

647
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:49,220
I feel guilty using things

648
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:50,670
I didn't pay for.

649
00:23:51,410 --> 00:23:52,410
I'm leaving for the day.

650
00:23:52,930 --> 00:23:54,260
I'll take these blueberries with me.

651
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:02,920
See you tomorrow.

652
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,040
Bye.

653
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:07,990
160.

654
00:24:11,860 --> 00:24:13,580
Ms. Lawyer, you're back early today.

655
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:15,350
Are you cooking?

656
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,560
I haven't cooked for a long time.

657
00:24:18,580 --> 00:24:20,170
I don't know if it suits your taste.

658
00:24:21,770 --> 00:24:22,490
Is it too hot?

659
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:23,440
It's salty.

660
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:24,090
Salty?

661
00:24:24,110 --> 00:24:24,620
A bit salty.

662
00:24:24,650 --> 00:24:26,160
How about I adjust it a bit?

663
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:28,350
It's fine, I like whatever you make.

664
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:30,000
Alright, then hurry and wash your hands.

665
00:24:32,230 --> 00:24:32,990
This soup is not bad.

666
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:33,790
Yeah?

667
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:35,350
It's pretty tasty.

668
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,480
Alright, you should eat too.

669
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,830
Quanquan, I need to tell you something.

670
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:42,610
Go ahead.

671
00:24:46,050 --> 00:24:47,330
I'm not working at Liangcheng Law Firm anymore.

672
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:48,600
What happened?

673
00:24:49,280 --> 00:24:50,230
Liangcheng Law Firm...

674
00:24:50,900 --> 00:24:52,490
fired me and Luo Yingzi.

675
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:55,400
It was right after our wedding day.

676
00:24:55,940 --> 00:24:58,260
That's why I didn't have time to go on the honeymoon with you,

677
00:24:58,590 --> 00:25:01,620
and why I didn't get to go back to your hometown to host the wedding banquet.

678
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,280
But now we're back on track.

679
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:06,350
We've opened our own law firm,

680
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,370
called Yinghua Law Firm.

681
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:10,400
My name's in it too.

682
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:12,670
Although it was tough at first,

683
00:25:13,530 --> 00:25:15,640
we've started getting cases now.

684
00:25:16,450 --> 00:25:18,170
It'll get better step by step.

685
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,890
Don't worry.

686
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,820
Do you consider me your family?

687
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:25,790
Of course I do.

688
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,540
Then why didn't you tell me such a big thing

689
00:25:27,570 --> 00:25:29,610
the day after we got married?

690
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:36,360
I thought I could handle it myself,

691
00:25:36,390 --> 00:25:37,760
so I didn't tell you.

692
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:41,550
Forget it.

693
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,160
I won't explain.

694
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,270
Actually,

695
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:48,720
I've always relied on myself since I was a child.

696
00:25:48,930 --> 00:25:50,590
So, the more I face challenges,

697
00:25:52,050 --> 00:25:54,100
the less I want to talk to others about it,

698
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:56,990
for fear that

699
00:25:57,590 --> 00:25:59,260
I'll become a burden to them.

700
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:01,460
Am I someone else?

701
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:03,310
I'm your husband.

702
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,550
We're going to spend our lives together.

703
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,310
I'm sorry.

704
00:26:10,370 --> 00:26:11,480
Stop it. Let's eat.

705
00:26:31,850 --> 00:26:33,570
Now that things have come to this,

706
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:37,160
let's take it one step at a time.

707
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:43,410
Xia Shu, you're back.

708
00:26:45,250 --> 00:26:46,250
What happened?

709
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,180
Xia Shu's dad

710
00:26:49,490 --> 00:26:50,820
was officially arrested. And then?

711
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:52,640
And she

712
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:55,000
wants to go back and be her father's attorney.

713
00:26:55,300 --> 00:26:56,270
But her dad

714
00:26:56,670 --> 00:26:57,750
strongly disagrees.

715
00:27:00,470 --> 00:27:02,470
If it were me, I wouldn't agree either.

716
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,200
My dad

717
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:11,070
did make a huge mistake,

718
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:13,640
but...

719
00:27:15,170 --> 00:27:16,730
But he's my dad.

720
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:19,680
He loves me.

721
00:27:21,190 --> 00:27:22,470
Now that he's in trouble,

722
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:24,870
there's nothing I can do to help.

723
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,310
Xia Shu,

724
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:29,050
you should know

725
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:30,310
your own abilities.

726
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:33,360
Since it has already happened,

727
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,440
crying won't help.

728
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:37,730
You should think of a solution quickly.

729
00:27:38,150 --> 00:27:39,310
Have you hired a lawyer?

730
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:41,840
Yes.

731
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:42,960
Xia Shu,

732
00:27:43,540 --> 00:27:45,660
now you should realize that you need to work hard.

733
00:27:46,330 --> 00:27:48,000
Your parents raised you.

734
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:49,680
When the family faces trouble,

735
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,670
you have to be able to support it,

736
00:27:52,690 --> 00:27:53,370
understand?

737
00:27:58,660 --> 00:27:59,660
Go wash your face.

738
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:01,030
Okay.

739
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:06,030
Qiu Hua.

740
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,030
Sit here. Let me tell you something.

741
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:14,110
The 800,000 yuan Xia Shu got from selling that car—

742
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:16,790
after paying for Auntie Song's lawsuit fees—

743
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,560
was all

744
00:28:19,010 --> 00:28:19,640
used to

745
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:22,560
hire a lawyer for her father.

746
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:25,790
So, that means we don't have any money left.

747
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:28,610
As for Auntie Song's case,

748
00:28:28,630 --> 00:28:29,870
we don't even know when the court hearing will be,

749
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:31,160
let alone

750
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,750
if we can make any money from it.

751
00:28:33,870 --> 00:28:35,830
As for the case your senior introduced,

752
00:28:36,010 --> 00:28:37,920
even if the negotiations go smoothly,

753
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,440
at most

754
00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:41,440
we'll only get 30,000.

755
00:28:43,150 --> 00:28:44,590
We can't keep going like this.

756
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:46,430
I've thought about it.

757
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,400
How about we have Xia Shu

758
00:28:49,010 --> 00:28:50,640
handle Auntie Song's case herself?

759
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,270
In terms of work,

760
00:28:52,290 --> 00:28:53,860
it will give her some experience,

761
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:55,770
and in terms of life,

762
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:57,750
it'll help distract her a bit

763
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:59,550
during this time.

764
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,200
As for us,

765
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:03,730
let's see if there are any other cases we can take on

766
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:04,690
to support ourselves.

767
00:29:05,180 --> 00:29:06,360
Okay, no problem.

768
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:12,790
The car is over there.

769
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:14,920
It'll be yours for the next couple of days.

770
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,190
Okay.

771
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:19,770
Xia Shu.

772
00:29:22,290 --> 00:29:23,270
Remember:

773
00:29:24,110 --> 00:29:25,920
right now, you have no right to pity others.

774
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,580
You don't know how pitiful you look

775
00:29:27,610 --> 00:29:28,370
in others' eyes.

776
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:30,450
As long as you catch them,

777
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:32,960
you must get the subpoena into their hands, no matter what.

778
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:33,760
Don't worry.

779
00:29:34,070 --> 00:29:35,110
They're not kids.

780
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:37,290
They should know that avoiding won't solve anything.

781
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:38,660
I'm leaving.

782
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,120
Xia Shu.

783
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:46,200
You've really grown up.

784
00:29:50,630 --> 00:29:51,320
Be careful.

785
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,270
It's this one.

786
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:13,090
The "for rent" sign is on it.

787
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:22,000
Hello, the number you dialed is not in service.

788
00:30:22,150 --> 00:30:23,710
Please check and dial again.

789
00:30:27,370 --> 00:30:28,740
What are you doing?

790
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,480
Sorry for the disruption.

791
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:35,570
It's not in service.

792
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,030
Who are you guys?

793
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:40,450
I'm from the Chengdong District People's Court.

794
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:41,850
Where are the people in this company?

795
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:44,080
I heard they were sued a couple of days ago and have run off.

796
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:44,960
Sir,

797
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,790
do you know how I can contact them?

798
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:47,790
How would I know?

799
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:00,380
-Is that it?
-They're coming.

800
00:31:00,520 --> 00:31:01,440
Ms. Xia.

801
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:06,830
Damin.

802
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,200
I'm going in to grab something.

803
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,190
I'll be right back. Wait for me.

804
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:10,110
Ms. He Qiaohui!

805
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:11,640
We're from the People's Court!

806
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,440
We're here to deliver your summons!

807
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:13,440
-Don't go!
-Hurry up! Let's go!

808
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,110
Don't go!

809
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:21,190
You weren't there.

810
00:31:21,530 --> 00:31:22,720
Let me tell you, that scene...

811
00:31:22,930 --> 00:31:24,670
Young people chasing the car is one thing,

812
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,550
but she's over seventy,

813
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,640
and she was also chasing it.

814
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,030
Stop!

815
00:31:30,570 --> 00:31:32,440
That was putting money over life!

816
00:31:35,230 --> 00:31:37,200
I've been a lawyer for many years.

817
00:31:37,290 --> 00:31:38,960
I've seen all kinds of people.

818
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,330
Are you alright, Auntie Song?

819
00:31:42,990 --> 00:31:43,750
This person...

820
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:46,400
is really evil.

821
00:31:48,010 --> 00:31:48,860
If you ask me,

822
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:50,460
it has to be Mr. Han.

823
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,750
No matter how difficult the case,

824
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,240
he can handle it.

825
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:57,830
But...

826
00:31:58,370 --> 00:31:59,090
Mr. Han,

827
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,590
we can't...

828
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:03,310
keep hiding,

829
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:03,830
right?

830
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:06,960
It's tough for the court, and it's tough for us, too.

831
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,200
Besides,

832
00:32:08,550 --> 00:32:10,160
if we keep hiding like this,

833
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:11,320
what about our business?

834
00:32:12,650 --> 00:32:13,550
Mr. Han,

835
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,720
you told us to hide, and we did it, right?

836
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,440
But we can't keep hiding forever.

837
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:18,980
You've got to think of another way.

838
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,440
Well,

839
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:22,230
there are other ways, of course.

840
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:25,160
But your case

841
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:27,000
is very complicated.

842
00:32:27,670 --> 00:32:28,990
Last time, I acted on my own

843
