00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,320
Okay, no problem.

1123
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,280
Alright, let's go.

1124
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:10,050
Wait a minute.

1125
00:41:10,690 --> 00:41:11,250
Well...

1126
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,830
If we refer the case

1127
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:14,220
to someone else,

1128
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,840
we may need to charge a small...

1129
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:19,160
referral fee.

1130
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:22,650
Mr. Tian.

1131
00:41:23,030 --> 00:41:24,920
I transferred 2,000 yuan to you.

1132
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:27,700
You're too kind.

1133
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,030
Come in.

1134
00:41:35,870 --> 00:41:36,470
Shuo.

1135
00:41:39,180 --> 00:41:40,570
What did you call me, Tian?

1136
00:41:40,970 --> 00:41:41,930
Shuo.

1137
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:44,790
"Mr. Chen" sounds too formal.

1138
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:45,440
Calling you "Shuo" is more friendly.

1139
00:41:45,470 --> 00:41:46,700
We're close, aren't we?

1140
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:48,500
What happened?

1141
00:41:53,530 --> 00:41:54,440
My stomach hurts.

1142
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,210
Excuse me.

1143
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:01,550
Is he good?

1144
00:42:01,870 --> 00:42:03,750
He's just a kid who hasn't grown up yet.

1145
00:42:04,020 --> 00:42:05,350
He's definitely not as talented as you.

1146
00:42:05,370 --> 00:42:06,210
Of course.

1147
00:42:07,030 --> 00:42:07,590
But Shuo,

1148
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,070
you can't be too careless.

1149
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:10,400
He can prepare

1150
00:42:10,550 --> 00:42:11,670
for exams anywhere.

1151
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:13,550
Why does he have to do it in your office?

1152
00:42:13,930 --> 00:42:15,840
It's definitely because Ms. Fang doesn't trust you

1153
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,380
and arranged for him to keep an eye on you.

1154
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:19,040
That's not necessary.

1155
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:20,880
What is there to monitor about me?

1156
00:42:20,880 --> 00:42:22,510
I'm just sitting here and working diligently.

1157
00:42:22,530 --> 00:42:23,700
She sent me an assistant

1158
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,970
to run errands for me.

1159
00:42:24,990 --> 00:42:25,880
I'm quite comfortable.

1160
00:42:26,370 --> 00:42:27,730
Don't say things like that.

1161
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,360
Let's get down to business.

1162
00:42:29,770 --> 00:42:32,200
I just mentioned the fake divorce

1163
00:42:32,470 --> 00:42:33,440
to those two clients.

1164
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:36,200
They agreed

1165
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:38,390
and even asked me to introduce a lawyer to them.

1166
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:39,490
But...

1167
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,760
Shuo, as you know,

1168
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:43,280
I don't know any other lawyers

1169
00:42:43,310 --> 00:42:45,270
except for those at our law firm.

1170
00:42:45,820 --> 00:42:47,780
So, could you recommend one to me?

1171
00:42:49,070 --> 00:42:50,000
Isn't it a bit inappropriate?

1172
00:42:50,090 --> 00:42:51,860
Isn't this taking someone else's benefit?

1173
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:53,110
You came up with this idea.

1174
00:42:53,490 --> 00:42:54,130
Don't say that.

1175
00:42:54,840 --> 00:42:55,550
Shuo,

1176
00:42:55,660 --> 00:42:57,270
you've got to recommend one to me.

1177
00:42:57,710 --> 00:43:00,030
How about this? Once we win the case,

1178
00:43:00,050 --> 00:43:01,340
I'll ask them for a referral fee,

1179
00:43:01,640 --> 00:43:02,640
and I'll give you

1180
00:43:03,760 --> 00:43:04,550
one-third of it.
